# Sofia Hotel Receptionist - Production Voice Agent

## üè® Professional Hotel Front Desk AI

Sofia is a **voice-only hotel receptionist** powered by local AI technology. Perfect for hotel front desks, guest services, and reception areas.

### ‚ú® Key Features
- **üé§ Voice-Only Interface** - No text input, pure voice interaction
- **üîí Private & Secure** - Runs entirely on local hardware
- **üè® Hotel Specialized** - 50+ booking and service tools
- **üåç Professional** - Natural hospitality responses
- **‚ö° Real-Time** - Instant voice processing and responses

### üîß Technology Stack
- **Speech Recognition:** Moonshine STT (State-of-the-art)
- **Voice Synthesis:** Kokoro TTS (Natural human-like voice)
- **AI Brain:** Ollama Gemma3 4B (Local LLM)
- **Voice Processing:** FastRTC (Real-time audio)

## üöÄ Quick Start

### Requirements
- Microphone for guest voice input
- Speakers for Sofia's voice output
- Local voice AI environment (already configured)

### Launch Sofia Receptionist

**Option 1: Pure Console Mode (Recommended for Production)**
```bash
cd /Users/tolga/Desktop/elvi/sofia-pers/sofia-hotel/agents/hotel
/Users/tolga/Desktop/elvi/sofia-pers/local-voice-ai-agent/.venv/bin/python sofia_hotel_receptionist.py receptionist
```
- Direct microphone/speaker interaction
- No browser required
- Perfect for hotel front desk kiosk

**Option 2: Web Interface Mode (For Testing/Monitoring)**
```bash
cd /Users/tolga/Desktop/elvi/sofia-pers/sofia-hotel/agents/hotel
/Users/tolga/Desktop/elvi/sofia-pers/local-voice-ai-agent/.venv/bin/python sofia_hotel_web.py receptionist
```
- Opens in browser with visual interface
- Shows conversation in real-time
- Good for staff monitoring

